		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="406" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷海马进行一次环转，造成<span color="#ffacff">60%</span><span>伤害；无珍珠时进行则造成</span><span color="#bababa">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷海马从远处迅速冲向玩家，造成<span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害；途经将留下雷曜地面，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">6%</span><span>伤害；无珍珠时进行则造成</span><span color="#bababa">65%</span><span>伤害，且不会留下雷曜地面。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷海马迅速翻滚至多3圈，分别造成<span color="#ffacff">60%,60%,50%</span><span>伤害；无珍珠时进行则造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">50%,50%,40%</span><span>伤害；攻击造成的伤害带有(1,0.5)的衰减。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="422" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷海马释放出大群的游鱼，游鱼在飞出一小会后冲向玩家，造成<span color="#ffacff">35%,17.5%,<br/>6.3%~3.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="422" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷海马登天，朝玩家猛地下戳，造成<span color="#ffacff">95%</span><span>伤害，并引起地裂喷涌，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，留下雷曜地面。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1087" width="429" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当珍珠盾量&lt;=7时施放；雷海马登天，唤临3枚<span textDecoration="underline">共鸣珊瑚珠</span><span>，并不断降下总计5道的落雷，均造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害。<br/>破坏所有珊瑚珠可以使其瘫痪陷入无珠状态，未及时破除会修复珍珠。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷海马瞄准并锁定玩家，数秒后在玩家处产生喷涌，造成<span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，留下雷曜地面，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1087" width="427" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">陷入无珠状态约<span color="#dfbfff">30s/20s(深境螺旋)</span><span>后，雷海马即将再度生成</span><span textDecoration="underline">异海珍珠</span><span>！生成时施放雷暴，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/千年珍珠骏麟.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="138">
