		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#8d29b4" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#8d29b4">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1188" width="428" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">异海珍珠：<span color="#ffacff">19雷</span><span>盾，击破使其进入无珠状态；免疫扩散附着；第二次及后续再生时只有</span><span color="#ffacff">11.4雷</span><span>盾。<br/>共鸣珊瑚珠：</span><span color="#ffacff">0.4雷</span><span>盾，击破扣除异海珍珠当前剩余-</span><span color="#ffacff">当前/3雷</span><span>，若未及时破除，每个珍珠则将恢复异海珍珠</span><span color="#ffacff">当前/3+2雷</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
